00:13:59,099 --> 00:14:01,181
Like, they literally fixed it, pushed the patch,

210
00:14:01,341 --> 00:14:03,203
and I responded to this person in an hour.

211
00:14:03,643 --> 00:14:04,564
They were really impressed.

212
00:14:04,684 --> 00:14:08,027
And it just helps to show you that you're listening

213
00:14:08,427 --> 00:14:11,670
and that you actually care about, yeah,

214
00:14:11,770 --> 00:14:12,751
the impact your game has.

