254
00:16:28,595 --> 00:16:30,676
and they will help you make your game better,

255
00:16:31,697 --> 00:16:33,698
if you listen to the right ones.

256
00:16:35,384 --> 00:16:39,525
Um, yeah, you can, as I said, you can receive and implement that feedback.

257
00:16:40,586 --> 00:16:45,627
Early on, I made a Trello board, which was a public issue tracker, and we had a

