00:16:46,288 --> 00:16:52,110
lot of the most common bugs and issues on there and the players could go on there

259
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:56,551
and see what the progress was with those, whether we were like fixing them or

260
00:16:56,611 --> 00:17:01,312
whether they were fixed yet, which really helped and that helped to prevent a lot

