00:17:01,353 --> 00:17:04,073
of repeated questions as well, especially in the Discord.

262
00:17:05,298 --> 00:17:09,341
It helps you to build a really strong community and create brand advocates.

263
00:17:10,141 --> 00:17:14,283
And it also helps you to develop your brand image if you're a new company.

264
00:17:15,284 --> 00:17:19,986
So for Ponko, I believe that we're quite quirky, grounded and responsive company.

265
00:17:20,907 --> 00:17:26,030
And making sure you listen to your players creates a lot of goodwill.

266
00:17:26,290 --> 00:17:28,691
Like I feel like they trust us and they know that we're going to

267
00:17:28,711 --> 00:17:29,672
listen to what they have to say.

268
00:17:32,427 --> 00:17:38,715
There's also many challenges of early access, such as constant changes with the game, which

269
00:17:38,795 --> 00:17:41,318
means I was making a lot of content last minute.

270
00:17:42,739 --> 00:17:49,627
